originalText.text: Victoria Benatar is a talented and professional architect, that will add tremendous  value and usage to any space. I highly recommend her services and sense of style.  She is dedicated and responsive to every client and will provide noticeable results within a reasonable budget. As a mortgage banker I have received glowing remarks from clients I referred to her past.

originalText.text:
A strong background in business, and client attention is the foundation of what makes Victoria so successful.
Victoria Benatar is driven by the understanding that a client’s needs are paramount, especially when the goal is as substantial as that of one’s dream project. Whether working with a New Yorker or an international concern seeking innovative ideas, Victoria ensures the highest level of integrity, dedication, knowledge, diligence and transparency.
She is selfless in her work, honest in her intentions and particularly devoted to her clients’ needs
Victoria is an ambitious, effective visionary and highly organized multi-tasker, she streamlines the design process for every client she represents. Her tenacity and persistence are vital assets in getting projects completed on time.
She will only guide her clients with information, expertise and open communication so one proceeds through the process with educated confidence.

Albert Attias
Director of Retail Business Development for Steve Madden, Ltd

originalText.text: I know Victoria from many years and I had the opportunity to see her work closely. Victoria is organized, efficient, and extremely competent, she is a very talented architect. I really enjoyed see her work; especially when she works in spaces that required a change and transform them is a beautiful spaces. The commitment and energy that she applies to her work is amazing. I highly recommend her!!!
